articles.author: Somshuvra Laha
articles.title: All-round Stoinis stars in 39-run win for Australia - Hindustan Times
articles.description: Australia overcome slow start riding allrounder’s 36-ball 67 and 3/19 to defeat Oman | Crickit
articles.content: On expected lines, Oman were no match for Australia, even though a 39-run margin isnt considered big enough for T20 cricket these days. It could have been though, had Ayaan Khan not lost his balance … [+2431 chars]
